As following the bug [JRA-27777|https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRA-27777], the top level label in the Base URL accept using like .loc but not the digital character like .2c but according to the [RFC 2396|http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2396]: 
{code}
   toplabel      = alpha | alpha *( alphanum | "-" ) alphanum
{code}
The top level label should accept the digital character.

